{"prompt": "Generate a website for a health and wellness app. The website should be vibrant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Wellness Bloom</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #3498db;\n            --secondary-color: #eaf2f8;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), #2980b9);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 80px 0;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            